title: Wednesday Post Show (01-26-22)
itunes:title: Wednesday Post Show (01-26-22)
description:
Bobby starts by running through some voicemails from listeners. We also talk about the NFL standings and if Tom Brady will retire. Bobby talks about a lesson his uncle taught him about gambling. A man who won $2 million dollars playing numbers he got from a fortune cookie. Bobby reads emails from listeners who were upset about Lunchbox’s Top 25 Most Famous people in Country music. Amy had a similar experience to Bobby’s ghost dog…she saw a guy dressed in white in her yard.
